# Environment Variables for Paywise Frontend

Copy this file to `.env` in the frontend directory and update the values for your environment.

## API Configuration

# Production API URL
EXPO_PUBLIC_API_URL=https://api.yourdomain.com/api

# Development API URLs (choose based on your platform)
# For iOS Simulator:
# EXPO_PUBLIC_API_URL=http://localhost:8000/api

# For Android Emulator:
# EXPO_PUBLIC_API_URL=http://10.0.2.2:8000/api

# For Physical Device (use your computer's local IP):
# EXPO_PUBLIC_API_URL=http://192.168.1.100:8000/api

## Other Configuration (Optional)
# EXPO_PUBLIC_APP_NAME=Paywise
# EXPO_PUBLIC_API_TIMEOUT=30000
